I guess, in so many words,
I'm a pro at that in my mind.

34:09.462 --> 34:13.056
The Trojans were led on the
court all season by 6'2'"sophomore guard...

34:13.166 --> 34:15.065
Curtis Gates.

34:25.812 --> 34:30.181
When he went to college,
and Michael Jordan first came to the NBA...

34:30.283 --> 34:34.878
they would, you know, sit around and argue
over him-who could play the best.

34:37.656 --> 34:42.059
Curtis was named Player
of the Decade at Colby Junior College...

34:42.161 --> 34:45.824
but he also developed a reputation
for being uncoachable.

34:46.864 --> 34:51.529
Curtis's idea of being real good is...

34:51.637 --> 34:55.664
you don't follow the rules,
you do what you wanna do.

34:55.774 --> 35:00.040
Curtis finally signed
at the University of Central Florida...

35:00.145 --> 35:03.773
but he didn't get along with the coach
and rarely played.

35:03.881 --> 35:06.406
Even if he didn't play ball...

35:06.517 --> 35:08.117
it was a nice university.

35:08.119 --> 35:10.646
He could have finished school.

35:10.755 --> 35:12.655
But he couldn't handle it.

35:23.034 --> 35:25.161
Security. Can I help you?

35:25.269 --> 35:28.238
I'm used to everybody
in the neighborhood loving me...

35:28.339 --> 35:30.637
and knowing how good I can play.

35:31.743 --> 35:33.158
It just seemed like people looked up

35:33.159 --> 35:35.007
to Curtis Gates when
it came to basketball...

35:35.112 --> 35:37.205
but now...

35:37.314 --> 35:39.839
I'm just a regular old guy
on the street now.

35:52.028 --> 35:54.622
Welcome to the prep game of the week...

35:54.731 --> 35:56.631
in the Class AA Sectional Final.

35:56.733 --> 36:00.066
You got the guru,
the legend, in Gene Pingatore.

36:00.170 --> 36:02.660
Gates.! Good.!

36:02.772 --> 36:05.536
Boy, Gates is on fire.

36:05.641 --> 36:07.609
William Gates is one
of the premier sophomores.

36:07.710 --> 36:10.543
William scores
17 points in the first half...

36:10.646 --> 36:14.377
as the Chargers look to return
to the state finals.

36:14.483 --> 36:17.145
Gates.

36:17.253 --> 36:19.221
Good.!

36:20.756 --> 36:23.020
He is a thoroughbred of a player.

36:26.929 --> 36:29.159
Can they get it done here now?

36:29.265 --> 36:32.631
In the second half, Gordon Tech
turns to their own sophomore star.

