But I just pushed myself
to come out here...

40:08.676 --> 40:12.009
because I know, in the long run,
it's gonna be good for myself...

40:12.113 --> 40:14.843
and for my family.

40:16.050 --> 40:18.883
I give my mother $50
out of my checks.

40:19.920 --> 40:22.512
All she done for me, I
don't think there ever

40:22.513 --> 40:24.879
be enough that I can
get to pay her back.

