02:04:12.074 --> 02:04:13.974
- Good luck.
- All right. You too.

02:04:37.965 --> 02:04:41.731
Marshall's second-round opponent,
Manley, presents little challenge.

02:04:41.836 --> 02:04:45.169
This just explains a little bit
about our program...

02:04:45.273 --> 02:04:47.468
where our program's headed.

02:04:47.575 --> 02:04:50.203
I like what you're sayin;
and I want him close to home.

02:04:50.311 --> 02:04:52.404
- Yeah.
- You know. And, uh -

02:04:52.513 --> 02:04:54.845
I think, you know -
I'm kind of leaning your way...

02:04:54.949 --> 02:04:57.771
because I just thank God
that he's getting into it -

02:04:57.772 --> 02:04:59.476
you know, somebody do want him.

