02:05:08.929 --> 02:05:10.453
Us Arts gotta stick together.

02:05:10.563 --> 02:05:11.962
- I'm over at Kennedy-King.
- Kennedy-King?

02:05:12.065 --> 02:05:13.965
- Yeah.
- Okay.

02:05:14.067 --> 02:05:16.160
May the best man win.

02:05:16.269 --> 02:05:19.898
- I thought mom was a cheerleader.
- Oh, thanks.

02:05:21.141 --> 02:05:23.109
Thank you for the compliment.

02:05:23.209 --> 02:05:27.008
His parents seem to think
he may, uh, pass the A.C.T.

02:05:27.112 --> 02:05:29.410
- he may what?
- He may pass it.

02:05:29.515 --> 02:05:31.983
Oh, yeah.
Well, I hope he does.

02:05:32.084 --> 02:05:34.609
- Us Arts gotta stick together, guy.
- Yeah.

02:05:36.288 --> 02:05:38.085
- Okay.
- Hey.

02:05:38.190 --> 02:05:41.353
Would you get excited if a college coach
came up and talked to you?

02:05:42.394 --> 02:05:44.362
Not really.

02:05:45.397 --> 02:05:47.297
Really, it's just-
